@baseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:8080
@json = application/json
@taskId = task-tracking-select-merged-002

### Tracking manual selection merged test
### Goal:
### 1) auto-send manual selection request when multiple targets are detected
### 2) system starts 20s timer after request
### 3) if feedback arrives within 20s -> track designated target
### 4) if no feedback in 20s -> default to highest-score target
### 5) keep verification steps aligned with tracking_escort.http:
###    planning callback, autonomy dispatch, optical linkage, media stream logs
###
### Important:
### - This script is one merged scenario with two optional branches.
### - Execute only one branch (A or B) after step 11.
### - If you need strict "report up to 4 sorted candidates", set:
###   config/service_settings.yaml -> tracking.filter.top_k_candidates: 4
###   then restart service.

### 1. Reset local mock state
POST {{baseUrl}}/mock/dds/reset

### 2. Set ownship initial state
POST {{baseUrl}}/mock/dds/navigation
Content-Type: {{json}}

{
  "platform_id": 1001,
  "speed_mps": 6.2,
  "heading_deg": 90.0,
  "longitude": 120.5000000,
  "latitude": 30.2200000,
  "timestamp": "2026-04-01T10:00:00Z"
}

