### 4. Create tracking task in escort mode (without explicit target_id)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/tasks
Content-Type: {{json}}

{
  "task_id": "{{taskId}}",
  "task_type": "tracking",
  "task_name": "tracking-select-merged-test",
  "task_source": "planning_service",
  "priority": 1,
  "mode": "escort",
  "target_info": {
    "target_type_code": 106
  },
  "task_area": {
    "area_type": "polygon",
    "points": [
      { "longitude": 121.49, "latitude": 31.21 },
      { "longitude": 121.55, "latitude": 31.21 },
      { "longitude": 121.55, "latitude": 31.24 },
      { "longitude": 121.49, "latitude": 31.24 }
    ]
  },
  "expected_speed": 12.0,
  "update_interval_sec": 1,
  "end_condition": {
    "duration_sec": 300,
    "out_of_region_finish": true
  },
  "linkage_param": {
    "enable_optical": true,
    "enable_evidence": true
  }
}

### 5. Inspect planning plan reports
GET {{baseUrl}}/mock/collaboration/planning/plans

### 6. Simulate planning feasibility callback
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/tasks/callbacks/planning/feasibility
Content-Type: {{json}}

{
  "task_id": "{{taskId}}",
  "plan_type": "patrol",
  "feasible": true,
  "reason": "route accepted by planning",
  "suggested_action": "continue",
  "callback_time": "2026-04-01T10:00:05Z"
}

### 7. Inspect candidate ranking and current selected target
### Expected: current_target_id is highest-score candidate by default
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/tasks/{{taskId}}/result

### 8. Inspect autonomy tracking dispatch logs (before manual selection)
GET {{baseUrl}}/mock/autonomy/tracking/logs

### 2. Set ownship initial state
POST {{baseUrl}}/mock/dds/navigation
Content-Type: {{json}}

{
  "platform_id": 1001,
  "speed_mps": 6.2,
  "heading_deg": 90.0,
  "longitude": 121.5000000,
  "latitude": 31.2200000,
  "timestamp": "2026-04-01T10:00:00Z"
}

### 9. Inspect auto-generated manual selection request logs
GET {{baseUrl}}/mock/collaboration/manual-selection/requests

### 10. Inspect manual selection status (auto-send + 20s timer state)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/tasks/{{taskId}}/manual-selection/status

### 11. Choose one branch below (A or B), do not execute both


### ====================
### Branch A: feedback in 20s -> track designated target
### ====================

### A1. Send feedback within 20 seconds from request_time in status endpoint
### Pick a non-top candidate intentionally to verify override
### Note: feedback_time is recorded only; timeout check uses server current time.
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/tasks/manual-selection/feedback
Content-Type: {{json}}

{
  "task_id": "{{taskId}}",
  "selected_target_id": "target-select-003",
  "feedback_time": "2026-04-01T00:00:00Z"
}

### A2. Inspect manual selection feedback logs
GET {{baseUrl}}/mock/collaboration/manual-selection/feedbacks

### A3. Verify task follows designated target
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/tasks/{{taskId}}/result

### A4. Inspect autonomy tracking dispatch after designated selection
GET {{baseUrl}}/mock/autonomy/tracking/logs


### ====================
### Branch B: no feedback in 20s -> default highest-score target
### ====================

### B1. Do not send feedback. Wait at least 20 seconds from request_time in status endpoint.

### B2. Verify task keeps/defaults to highest-score target
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/tasks/{{taskId}}/result

### B3. Verify status shows pending=false after timeout
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/tasks/{{taskId}}/manual-selection/status

### B4. Inspect autonomy tracking dispatch after timeout defaulting
GET {{baseUrl}}/mock/autonomy/tracking/logs


### ====================
### Shared post-selection checks (optical/media/autonomy like escort script)
### ====================

### 12. Inspect current local situation before manual arrival
GET {{baseUrl}}/mock/dds/situation

### 13. Simulate ownship arrival near dispatched tracking point
### Replace longitude/latitude with /api/v1/tasks/{{taskId}}/result -> recommended_point values
POST {{baseUrl}}/mock/dds/navigation
Content-Type: {{json}}

{
  "platform_id": 1001,
  "speed_mps": 6.2,
  "heading_deg": 90.0,
  "longitude": 121.50474193708843,
  "latitude": 31.219999893054922,
  "timestamp": "2026-04-01T10:00:20Z"
}

### 14. Inspect local situation after arrival
GET {{baseUrl}}/mock/dds/situation

### 15. Inspect emitted optical DDS commands (target lock expected)
GET {{baseUrl}}/mock/collaboration/optical-linkage/commands

### 16. Inspect media stream access logs (optical stream expected)
GET {{baseUrl}}/mock/collaboration/media/stream-access

### 17. Inspect task result after arrival
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/tasks/{{taskId}}/result

### 18. Move ownship away before terminate
POST {{baseUrl}}/mock/dds/navigation
Content-Type: {{json}}

{
  "platform_id": 1001,
  "speed_mps": 6.2,
  "heading_deg": 90.0,
  "longitude": 122.49,
  "latitude": 32.21,
  "timestamp": "2026-04-01T10:03:00Z"
}

### 19. Cleanup task
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/tasks/{{taskId}}/terminate
Content-Type: {{json}}

{
  "reason": "cleanup"
}





